title: ArcGIS Server License
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: GPL
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors ArcGIS Server license items.

 The check discovers license entries for Server edition, level, extensions, and
 features when returned by the Server admin API. It reports expiration status and
 feature validity when available.
item:
 The license item kind and name.
discovery:
 One service is discovered for each ArcGIS Server license item returned by the
 Server admin API.
perfdata:
 The check can emit days until expiration for expiring license items.
